0this%20regard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731049140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Findia-tailor-generic_650x400_81464845012.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-womens-body-proposes-men-shouldnt-tailor-womens-clothes-or-cut-their-hair-6971097%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Men%20should%20not%20tailor%20clothes%20for%20women%20or%20cut%20a%20woman's%20hair%20either%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20State%20Women%20Commission%20has%20proposed%20to%20protect%20women%20from%20%26quot%3Bbad%20touch%26quot%3B%20and%20stymie%20the%20ill%20intentions%20of%20men.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-womens-body-proposes-men-shouldnt-tailor-womens-clothes-or-cut-their-hair-6971097%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sony%20Pictures%20Profits%20Slip%20to%20%24124%20Million%20in%20Second%20Quarter%20as%20Group%20Makes%2075%25%20Leap%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731048985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2Fsony-corp-building-placeholder.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236204542%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sony%20Group%20Corporation%20reported%20little%20changed%20revenues%20of%20JPY2.91%20trillion%20for%20the%20July%20to%20September%20period%2C%20representing%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20its%20April%20to%20March%20financial%20year.%20But%20group-level%20net%20income%20surged%20by%2075%25%20to%20JPY3.39%20trillion.%20The%20%E2%80%98Pictures%20Division%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20spans%20the%20feature%20film%2C%20TV%20channels%20and%20TV%20content%20production%20operations%2C%20reported%20revenues%20of%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Patrick%20Frater%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fbiz%2Fnews%2Fsony-quarterly-results-pictures-profits-1236204542%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Private%20Property%20And%20The%20Question%20Of%20'Constitutional%20Socialism'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fdati4eas_supreme-court_160x120_06_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20an%20ideological%20dialogue%20happened%20in%20the%20Indian%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Article%2039(b)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20judgment%20by%20a%20nine-judge%20Bench%20in%20%3Cem%3EProperty%20Owners%20Association%20v.%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0last%20Tuesday%20reflects%20a%20division%20of%20opinion%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20though%20the%20majority%20on%20the%20Bench%20laid%20down%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstitutional%20socialism%2C%20like%20political%20socialism%2C%20has%20remained%20a%20controversial%20issue%20in%20the%20Indian%20juridical%20discourse.%20Article%2039(b)%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20together%20with%20other%20provisions%20under%20the%20directive%20principles%20in%20part%20IV%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20embodies%20an%20idea%20of%20constitutional%20socialism.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20contested%20argument.%20To%20understand%20the%20legal%20and%20political%20ramifications%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20let%20us%20now%20examine%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fundamentality%20Of%20Directive%20Principles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Court%20in%20the%20current%20case%20broadly%20did%20two%20things.%20First%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20annulment%20of%20certain%20amendments%20made%20to%20Article%2031-C%20of%20the%20Constitution%20would%20not%20nullify%20Article%2031-C%20in%20the%20unamended%20form.%20This%20is%20the%20Article%20that%20gives%20immunity%20to%20certain%20laws%20from%20judicial%20review%20if%20the%20laws%20are%20made%20to%20further%20the%20directive%20principles%20of%20state%20policy%20stated%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20Article%20says%20that%20such%20laws%20cannot%20be%20assailed%20on%20grounds%20of%20violation%20of%20the%20equality%20clause%20(Article%2014)%20or%20the%20freedom%20clause%20(Article%2019)%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20signifies%20the%20fundamentality%20of%20directive%20principles%20in%20the%20process%20of%20governance%2C%20which%20are%20otherwise%20not%20enforceable.%20This%20takes%20us%20to%20the%20second%20and%20the%20more%20vital%20part%20of%20the%20judgment.%20The%20majority%20held%20that%20the%20interpretation%20given%20to%20Article%2039(b)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20by%20Justice%20Krishna%20Iyer%20in%20a%20minority%20judgment%20in%201977%20in%20%3Cem%3ERanganatha%20Reddy%3C%2Fem%3E%20endorsed%20by%20the%20five-judge%20Bench%20in%20%3Cem%3ESanjeev%20Coke%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1982)%20was%20not%20good%20law%20on%20Article%2039(b).%20Thus%2C%20the%20Court%20overturned%20the%20precedential%20materials%20in%20the%20Article%20that%20gave%20an%20expanded%20connotation%20to%20this%20constitutional%20provision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2039(b)%20says%20that%20the%20State%20shall%20strive%20for%20policy%20to%20secure%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20ownership%20and%20control%20of%20the%20material%20resources%20of%20the%20community%20are%20so%20distributed%20as%20best%20to%20subserve%20the%20common%20good%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20minority%20judgment%20in%3Cem%3E%20State%20of%20Karnataka%20v.%20Ranganatha%20Reddy%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1977)%20Justice%20Krishna%20Iyer%20analysed%20the%20Article%20and%20said%20that%20all%20individual%20wealth%20is%20part%20of%20the%20community's%20wealth%20and%20therefore%2C%20private%20property%20is%20well%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmaterial%20resources%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmaterial%20resources%20of%20the%20community%20in%20the%20context%20of%20re-ordering%20the%20national%20economy%20embraces%20all%20the%20national%20wealth%2C%20not%20merely%20natural%20resources%2C%20all%20the%20private%20and%20public%20sources%20of%20meeting%20material%20needs%2C%20not%20merely%20public%20possessions%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cto%20exclude%20ownership%20of%20private%20resources%20from%20the%20coils%20of%20Article%2039(b)%20is%20to%20cipherise%20its%20very%20purpose%20of%20redistribution%20the%20socialist%20way%E2%80%9D.%20This%20minority%20verdict%20in%20%3Cem%3ERanganatha%20Reddy%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20endorsed%20by%20a%20five-judge%20Bench%20in%20Sanjeev%20Coke.%20Thus%2C%20the%20minority%20verdict%20%5Bwhich%20essentially%20has%20not%20expressly%20disagreed%20on%20the%20point%20of%20Article%2039(b)%5D%20got%20an%20authoritative%20endorsement%20in%20%3Cem%3ESanjeev%20Coke%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20interpretation%20was%20validated%20in%20a%20series%20of%20judgments%20that%20followed%20%3Cem%3ESanjeev%20Coke%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Thus%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9DKrishna%20Iyer%20doctrine%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20calls%20it%2C%20got%20judicially%20reaffirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Ambedkar%20Said%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20constitutional%20landscape%20that%20is%20now%20thoroughly%20altered%20by%20the%20majority%20judgment%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EProperty%20Owners%20Association%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecase.%20According%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20did%20not%20perceive%20the%20Article%20in%20the%20way%20Krishna%20Iyer%20did.%20Relying%20on%20the%20reply%20given%20by%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20to%20Prof.%20K.T.%20Shah%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20the%20Court%20is%20unable%20to%20subscribe%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20expensive%20view%E2%80%9D%20of%20Justice%20Iyer.%20He%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9D...(T)his%20Court%20must%20not%20tread%20into%20the%20domain%20of%20economic%20policy%2C%20or%20endorse%20a%20particular%20economic%20ideology%20while%20undertaking%20constitutional%20interpretation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counter%20view%20on%20Article%2039(b)%20is%20well%20reflected%20in%20Justice%20Dhulia's%20minority%20view.%20He%20endorses%20Krishna%20Iyer's%20approach%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20the%20Constitution%20in%20general%20and%20the%20directive%20principles%20%5Bincluding%20Article%2039(b)%5D%20are%20essentially%20socialist%20in%20their%20tone%20and%20tenor.%20Curiously%20again%2C%20Justice%20Dhulia%20relies%20on%20Dr%20Ambedkar's%20reply%20(relied%20on%20by%20Chandrachud)%20to%20say%20quite%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20very%20scheme%20of%20the%20directive%20principles%20reflected%20the%20idea%20of%20constitutional%20socialism.%20He%20also%20relied%20on%20Ambedkar's%20famous%20speech%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20November%2025%2C%201949%2C%20underscoring%20the%20absence%20of%20socio-economic%20equality%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20also%20put%20forward%20a%20blunt%20commonsensical%20reading%20of%20the%20Article%2C%20saying%20that%20for%20utilising%20public%20assets%20for%20public%20good%2C%20no%20constitutional%20provision%20is%20required%2C%20and%20the%20very%20purpose%20of%20Article%2039(b)%20is%20to%20empower%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20public%20good%20by%20resorting%20to%20privately%20owned%20resources.%20He%20said%20public%20property%20will%20be%20used%20for%20public%20good%20only%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20not%20contemplated%20in%20the%20directive%20principles.%20Criticism%20of%20the%20'Krishna%20Iyer%20doctrine'%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20is%20not%20endorsed%20by%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20either%2C%20though%20the%20judge%20agreed%20substantially%20with%20the%20majority%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELaw%2C%20Politics%2C%20And%20The%20'Iyer%20Doctrine'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20understand%20the%20constitutional%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20context%20in%20which%20the%20%E2%80%98Iyer%20doctrine'%20evolved.%20The%20era%20of%20Land%20Reforms%20Acts%20by%20different%20states%2C%20laws%20for%20abolition%20of%20the%20Zamindari%20system%20and%20privy%20purses%2C%20and%20nationalisation%20of%20private%20banks%20were%20all%20developments%20that%20facilitated%20a%20political%20climate%20of%20Nehruvian%20socialism%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20to%20the%20Krishna%20Iyer%20doctrine.%20Laws%20are%20essentially%20political%20statements%20made%20by%20the%20regime%20of%20the%20day.%20The%20preambular%20addition%20of%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Csocialist%E2%80%9D%20did%20not%20indicate%20anything%20new%20but%20only%20restated%20the%20socialist%20inclination%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20was%20otherwise%20clear%2C%20as%20elaborated%20by%20Justice%20Dhulia%20in%20the%20present%20minority%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20judgment%20also%20held%20that%20Article%2031-C%20in%20the%20unamended%20form%20will%20hold%20good.%20Certain%20additions%20to%20this%20Article%20made%20by%20way%20of%20the%2042nd%20amendment%20in%201977%20were%20struck%20down%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EMinerva%20Mills%20Case%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1980).%20The%20curious%20aspect%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20Centre%20argued%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20State's%20power%20to%20treat%20private%20properties%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmaterial%20resources%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%9D%2C%20relying%20on%20Krishna%20Iyer's%20doctrine.%20This%20argument%20was%20repelled%20by%20the%20majority%20on%20the%20Bench.%20In%20an%20era%20of%20privatisation%20of%20public%20properties%2C%20this%20gesture%20may%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20ironic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20any%20rate%2C%20the%20present%20regime%20at%20the%20Centre%20is%20not%20a%20proponent%20of%20Nehruvian%20socialism.%20Political%20and%20ideological%20shifts%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20determining%20what%20the%20Constitution%20means%2C%20what%20it%20says%20and%20how%20it%20is%20invoked.%20The%20distance%20that%20the%20nation%20has%20travelled%20since%201977%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%3Cem%3E%20Property%20Owners%20Association%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecase%20and%20the%20dissent%20in%20the%20judgment%20shows%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20coin.%20The%20judgment%20will%20carry%20forward%20the%20eternal%20discourse%20on%20the%20socialist%20traits%20in%20the%20country's%20Constitution.%20The%20juridical%20discourse%20on%20the%20topic%20underlines%20the%20quality%20of%20deliberative%20democracy%20within%20the%20system%20of%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kaleeswaram%20Raj%20is%20a%20lawyer%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731048960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fdati4eas_supreme-court_160x120_06_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fprivate-property-verdict-and-the-question-of-constitutional-socialism-6971090%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20distance%20that%20the%20nation%20has%20travelled%20since%201977%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20Property%20Owners%20Association%20case%20and%20the%20dissent%20in%20the%20judgment%20shows%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20coin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fprivate-property-verdict-and-the-question-of-constitutional-socialism-6971090%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'For%20ageing%20Rohit%20and%20Kohli%2C%20the%20true%20battle%20is%20against...'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publ