0rejected%20this%20demand%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20House%20itself%2C%20not%20the%20Speaker%2C%20held%20the%20authority%20to%20reverse%20any%20resolution%20passed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20speech%20by%20BJP's%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%2C%20Sunil%20Sharma%2C%20Awami%20Ittehad%20Party%20(AIP)%20leader%20Sheikh%20Khursheed%20entered%20the%20assembly%20well%2C%20holding%20a%20banner%20demanding%20the%20restoration%20of%20Articles%20370%20and%2035A.%20BJP%20legislators%20quickly%20intervened%2C%20snatching%20and%20tearing%20the%20banner%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20brief%20scuffle%20in%20which%20People's%20Conference%20MLA%20Sajad%20Lone%20supported%20Mr%20Khursheed.%20This%20followed%20a%2015-minute%20adjournment%20of%20the%20House.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20resumption%2C%20BJP%20members%20continued%20their%20protest%2C%20despite%20the%20Speaker's%20calls%20for%20order.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20force%20me%20to%20take%20actions%20I%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20take%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned%2C%20as%20BJP%20members%20persisted%20in%20chanting%20slogans%20honouring%20Bharatiya%20Jana%20Sangh%20founder%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee.%20Meanwhile%2C%20NC%20members%20responded%20with%20chants%20on%20the%20historic%20sacrifices%20made%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20escalated%20further%20when%20Speaker%20Rather%20ordered%20the%20removal%20of%20several%20protesting%20BJP%20members%2C%20prompting%20a%20physical%20confrontation%20with%20assembly%20marshals.%20Three%20BJP%20MLAs%20were%20eventually%20escorted%20out%2C%20while%20treasury%20bench%20members%20applauded%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20pointed%20address%2C%20Minister%20Satish%20Sharma%20condemned%20the%20BJP's%20actions%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20divisive%20tactics.%20Mr%20Sharma%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20MLAs%20had%20%26quot%3Bdisrespected%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B%20by%20allegedly%20standing%20on%20the%20document%20while%20protesting%2C%20cal