ates%20of%20%242.14.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENights%20and%20experiences%20booked%20jumped%208%25%20to%20122.8%20million%20from%20the%20same%20period%20in%202023.%20Bookings%20were%20slow%20early%20in%20the%20quarter%20but%20picked%20up%20later%2C%20CEO%20Brian%20Chesky%20said%20on%20Thursday's%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Airbnb%20were%204%25%20lower%20at%20%24141.55%20in%20after-hours%20trading%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228864efa4-c78c-476c-a7cc-e3f4be22aebc%5C%22%3EAirbnb%20wants%20to%20get%20more%20people%20to%20list%20properties%20using%20co-hosts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Airbnb%20started%20offering%20its%20hosts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.airbnb.com%2Fairbnb-2024-winter-release%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eco-hosts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20people%20who%20can%20help%20manage%20a%20property%20that's%20listed%20on%20Airbnb.%20The%20company%20launched%20its%20co-host%20network%20with%20about%2010%2C000%20people%20signed%20up%20for%20the%20role%20in%2010%20countries%2C%20Chesky%20said%20on%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20as%20Chesky%20said%2C%20is%20to%20make%20hosting%20on%20Airbnb%20less%20of%20a%20burden%20%E2%80%94%20and%20attract%20more%20hosts%20and%20properties%20to%20the%20platform.%20While%20many%20people%20are%20interested%20in%20listing%20their%20properties%20on%20Airbnb%2C%20many%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20the%20time%20managing%20the%20property%2C%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20we%20asked%20ourselves%2C%20what%20if%20we%20could%20match%20people%20with%20homes%20that%20don't%20have%20time%20with%20people%20that%20have%20extra%20time%20but%20don't%20have%20homes%3F%26quot%3B%20Chesky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20only%20would%20this%20unlock%20more%20supply%2C%20I%20think%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20this%20can%20unlock%20millions%20of%20listings%2C%26quot%3B%20Chesky%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d263d6c5-cd68-4