acility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%20of%20both%20The%20America%20First%20Warehouse%20and%20Corporate%20Transfer%2C%20Joseph%20Verderber%2C%20Jr.%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani's%20spokesman%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20has%20yet%20to%20turn%20over%20any%20of%20the%20possessions%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20last%20month%20to%20fulfill%20the%20%24148%20million%20defamation%20judgment%2C%20including%20a%20Mercedes%20once%20owned%20by%20Lauren%20Bacall%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bdiamond%20ring%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20several%20luxury%20watches%2C%20the%20plaintiff's%20attorney%2C%20Aaron%20Nathan%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20must%20also%20turn%20over%20%242%20million%20in%20legal%20fees%20he%20has%20previously%20said%20are%20owed%20to%20him%20by%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20money%20he%20said%20Thursday%20he%20still%20does%20not%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20complying%20with%20the%20order%20to%20surrender%20property%2C%20Giuliani%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bevasive%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsilent%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20moving%20cash%20around%2C%20including%20by%20opening%20bank%20accounts%20and%20forming%20a%20limited%20liability%20company%2C%20Nathan%20said%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20no%20longer%20has%20a%20possession%20right%20over%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Nathan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20asked%20over%20and%20over%20again%20where%20this%20stuff%20is.%20He%20refuses%20to%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20DiMaggio's%20jersey%20is%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20Rudy%20Giuliani's%20apartment%2C%20lawyers%20in%20his%20%24148M%20defamation%20case%20say.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672d2da4192f52589856d27e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20DiMaggio's%20jersey%20is%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20Rudy%20Giuliani's%20apartment%2C%20lawyers%20in%20his%20%24148M%20defamation%20case%20say.%3Cp%3EFreeman%20v.%20Giuliani%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20that%20if%20Freeman%20and%20Shaye%20believe%20the%20items%20from%20the%20New%20York%20apartment%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sports%20memorabilia%20he%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20couple%20of%20pictures%2C%20a%20shirt%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20were%20improperly%20moved%20and%20that%20Giuliani%20is%20lying%20about%20not%20being%20able%20to%20access%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Bthen%20plaintiffs%20can%20move%20for%20contempt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20can%20move%20for%20a%20contempt%20finding%20if%20Giuliani%20fails%20to%20comply%20with%20any%20of%20his%20court%20orders%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20client%20is%20not%20in%20possession%20of%20the%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20Giuliani's%20lawyer%20responded%2C%20to%20which%20the%20judge%20answered%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20in%20contempt%20if%20he's%20made%20attempts%20and%20it's%20impossible%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20order.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20after%20court%20what%20the%20holdup%20with%20the%20storage%20facility%20might%20be%2C%20Giuliani%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20didn't%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20they%20do%20is%20keep%20jerking%20us%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20smiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20was%20ordered%20Thursday%20to%20provide%20the%20plaintiffs'%20lawyers%20with%20the%20keys%20and%20title%20to%20the%20Mercedes%2C%20which%20the%20former%20mayor%20had%20tried%20to%20keep%20by%20saying%20its%20value%20was%20under%20%244%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%2054-year-old%20automobile%20is%20worth%20less%20than%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Caruso%20had%20argued%20again%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20was%20also%20ordered%20to%20continue%20working%20with%20the%20plaintiffs%20on%20getting%20access%20to%20the%20storage%20facility.%20He%20must%20also%20provide%20plaintiffs%20with%20current%20co-op%20shares%20for%20the%20Manhattan%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20had%20ordered%20Guiliani%20on%20October%2022%20to%20turn%20over%20many%20of%20his%20assets%2C%20including%20the%20apartment%2C%20the%20DiMaggio%20jersey%2C%20luxury%20wristwatches%2C%20and%20the%20Mercedes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-bankruptcy-dismissed-protection-year-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattempted%20to%20declare%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20a%20judge%20dismissed%20the%20case%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20jury%20in%202023%20awarded%20Freeman%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20Moss%2C%20%24148%20million%20to%20repair%20their%20lives%20after%20Guiliani%20peddled%20false%20claims%20that%20they%20manipulated%20ballots%20in%20the%202020%20election%20during%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20attempt%20to%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiuliani%20repeatedly%20said%20Freeman%20and%20her%20daughter%20pulled%20up%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%20ballots%20stashed%20in%20a%20suitcase%20and%20passed%20around%20a%20USB%20drive%20that%20contributed%20to%20Biden%20winning%20in%20Georgia%2C%20a%20key%20state%20in%20his%20electoral%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20received%20death%20threats%20and%20were%20subjected%20to%20harassment%20after%20Giuliani%20made%20his%20claims%20on%20social%20media%20and%20his%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Georgia%20state%20election%20board%20investigated%20the%20claims%20and%20cleared%20the%20women%20of%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frudy-giuliani-hiding-assets-election-workers-joe-dimaggio-apartment-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731025402000%2C%22