C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInvestors%20can%20use%20gold%20as%20a%20hedge%20against%20inflation%20and%20economic%20uncertainty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDiversifying%20with%20gold%20protects%20you%20against%20market%20downturns%20while%20helping%20preserve%20wealth.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBuy%20bullion%20coins%20and%20gold%20bars%20online%20with%20All%20American%20Assets.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price%5C%22%3E%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20surged%20to%20a%20record%20high%20in%20October%2C%20continuing%20a%20strong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-a-bull-market%5C%22%3Ebull%3C%2Fa%3E%20run%20that%20has%20persisted%20throughout%202024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGold%20was%20hitting%20price%20records%20even%20before%20the%20Fed%20started%20cutting%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Philip%20Patrick%2C%20precious%20metal%20specialist%20at%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-gold-ira%23best-for-investor-resources%5C%22%3E%20Birch%20Gold%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20explains%20that%20high%20global%20demand%20from%20central%20banks%20and%20general%20dollar%20devaluation%20since%20the%20pandemic%20has%20driven%20the%20price%20of%20gold.%20%26quot%3BInterest%20rates%20have%20an%20effect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20don't%20think%20they're%20the%20main%20driver%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20has%20historically%20underperformed%20compared%20to%20market-linked%20investments%20like%20stocks%20and%20index%20funds%20over%20the%20long%20run.%20Although%20it's%20not%20as%20profitable%20as%20higher-risk%20securities%2C%20experts%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-gold%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20best%20used%20as%20a%20means%20of%20further%20portfolio%20diversification%20and%20a%20hedge%20against%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsider%20adding%20gold%20to%20a%20diversified%20portfolio%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-diversification%5C%22%3EDiversification%3C%2Fa%3E%20aims%20to%20reduce%20portfolio%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Frisk-vs-volatility%5C%22%3E%20risk%20and%20volatility%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20investing%20in%20different%20asset%20classes.%20This%20strategy%20helps%20protect%20your%20portfolio%20from%20significant%20losses%20caused%20by%20the%20underperformance%20of%20a%20single%20investment.%20A%20more%20diverse%20portfolio%20is%20better%20equipped%20to%20weather%20market%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20general%20rule%20of%20thumb%20for%20diversifying%20your%20portfolio%20with%20precious%20metals%20is%20to%20invest%20between%205%25%20and%2010%25%20of%20your%20portfolio%20in%20physical%20gold.%20Although%20it%20varies%20from%20person%20to%20person%2C%20said%20Drew%20Martino%2C%20wealth%20manager%20at%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savvywealth.com%2Fadvisors%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Savvy%20Advisors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20generally%20does%20not%20recommend%20allocating%20more%20than%2010%25%20of%20any%20portfolio%20to%20alternative%20investments%2C%20including%20gold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20still%20a%20great%20time%20for%20the%20average%20investors%20to%20consider%20buying%20gold%20if%20they%20already%20have%20an%20established%20portfolio%20of%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%26quot%3B%20Martino%20said.%20However%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20recommend%20investing%20in%20just%20gold%20if%20you%20don't%20already%20own%20any%20other%20assets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20options%20to%20consider%20are%20gold%20ETFs%20and%20mutual%20funds.%20Compared%20to%20owning%20physical%20metal%2C%20gold%20funds%20offer%20greater%20liquidity.%20However%2C%20you%20don't%20actually%20own%20the%20gold.%20Moreover%2C%20you're%20still%20subject%20to%20mark%20risk%20as%20the%20value%20of%20your%20gold%20fund%20largely%20depends%20on%20the%20company%20managing%20the%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESustainable%20investing%20focuses%20on%20building%20a%20solid%20foundation%20with%20time-tested%20assets%20that%20withstand%20various%20market%20conditions.%20When%20diversifying%20your%20portfolio%20with%20gold%2C%20%26quot%3Bdo%20your%20due%20diligence%2C%20do%20your%20research%2C%20and%20get%20the%20information%20so%20you%20can%20go%20into%20it%20as%20informed%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrick%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20will%20put%20you%20in%20the%20best%20position.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can%20also%20use%20gold%20as%20an%20inflation%20hedge%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20faced%20with%20challenges%20like%20inflation%2C%20currency%20devaluation%2C%20or%20an%20impending%20recession%2C%20there's%20often%20an%20increased%20demand%20for%20safe-haven%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-are-commodities%5C%22%3E%20commodities%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20to%20preserve%20purchasing%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrick%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20gold%20is%20one%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Bsafe-haven%26quot%3B%20assets.%20As%20inflation%20erodes%20the%20dollar's%20purchasing%20power%2C%20driving%20up%20prices%2C%20gold%20tends%20to%20appreciate%2C%20making%20it%20an%20attractive%20investment%20for%20those%20seeking%20protection%20from%20market%20downturns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGold%20can%20still%20be%20volatile%2C%20but%20it%20has%20an%20intrinsic%20value%20and%20purchasing%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Martino.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20safe%20investment%20because%20it%20tends%20to%20fare%20better%20when%20stocks%20decline%20or%20during%20periods%20of%20inflation%2C%20but%20all%20investments%20hold%20some%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20gold%20isn't%20leverage.%20You%20won't%20generate%20income%20from%20dividends%20or%20interest.%20Price%20appreciation%20is%20the%20only%20way%20you%20can%20build%20wealth%20with%20physical%20gold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChuck%20Etzweiler%2C%20CFP%20and%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20research%20at%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnepsisinc.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Nepsis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cautioned%20against%20purchasing%20gold%20based%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20it's%20a%20viable%20strategy%20for%20building%20wealth.%20He%20recommends%20viewing%20gold%20as%20a%20currency%20hedge%20rather%20than%20an%20investment%20strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20gold%20bull%20run%20won't%20last%20forever%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20appreciates%20over%20time%2C%20making%20it%20an%20attractive%20investment%20for%20those%20seeking%20to%20lessen%20the%20impact%20of%20violent%20market%20swings.%20Over%20the%20long%20term%2C%20gold%20prices%20tend%20to%20rise%20due%20to%20sustained%20global%20demand.%20However%2C%20the%20US%20dollar's%20purchasing%20power%20will%20likely%20recover%20and%20eventually%20outpace%20gold%20as%20the%20economy%20strengthens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-the-sp-500%5C%22%3E%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20historically%20averaged%20an%20annual%20return%20of%20about%2010%25%20since%20its%20inception%20in%20the%201950s.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20index%20delivered%20an%20impressive%20annual%20return%20of%2026.3%25.%20In%20contrast%2C%20gold's%2010-year%20annualized%20return%20stands%20at%204.57%25%2C%20and%20its%202023%20annual%20return%20was%2013.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20greatest%20risk%20of%20investing%20in%20gold%20lies%20in%20the%20opportunity%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Patrick.%20%26quot%3BGold%20may%20underperform%20when%20the%20economy%20is%20strong%20compared%20to%20higher-yielding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-stocks%5C%22%3Estocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20market%20funds.%20While%20gold%20is%20a%20popular%20investment%2C%20investors%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20the%20accumulation%20phase%2C%20should%20avoid%20over-investing%20in%20any%20asset%2C%20including%20gold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-prices-soar-expert-tips-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731019141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672bdb665ec9b