tion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20to%20save%20by%20buying%20groceries%20instead%20of%20dining%20out%20every%20meal%2C%20but%20this%20didn't%20help%20much.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-grocery-store-food-prices-haawaii-eggs-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHawaii%20imports%20the%20majority%20of%20its%20groceries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20means%20they%20can%20get%20pricey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20grocery%20bill%20was%20%24101%2C%20but%20we%20still%20spent%20over%20%241%2C000%20on%20food%20and%20beverages%20at%20Aulani's%20various%20restaurants%20and%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20mostly%20ate%20at%20the%20property's%20more%20affordable%20restaurants.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Off%20the%20hook%20menu%20with%20cocktails%2C%20sandwiches%20being%20held%20by%20woman's%20hand%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671faebea0a0cc14f224579b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELike%20many%20restaurants%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20Aulani's%20menu%20items%20were%20pretty%20pricey.%20%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAulani%20has%20four%20table-service%20restaurants%20and%20a%20luau%20that%20includes%20dinner%20and%20a%20show.%20Food%20is%20also%20served%20at%20quick-service%20spots%20and%20snack%20kiosks%20at%20the%20pools%20and%20near%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20skipped%20Aulani's%20pricier%20sit-down%20restaurants%20with%20tasting%20menus%20%3Cspan%3EAMA'AMA%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20Makahiki.%20Instead%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20quick-service%20Ulu%20Cafe%20and%20casual%20outdoor%20eatery%20Off%20the%20Hook.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20food%20at%20Aulani%20was%20expensive.%20At%20Ulu%20Cafe%2C%20bagel%20sandwiches%20start%20at%20%2417%2C%20and%20most%20entr%C3%A9es%20at%20Off%20the%20Hook%20were%20over%20%2420.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20our%20order%20of%20two%20poke%20bowls%2C%20two%20small%20pizzas%2C%20and%20two%20water%20bottles%20cost%20us%20over%20%2490.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20booked%20one%20excursion%20through%20Aulani%20but%20it%20was%20pretty%20steep.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22USS%20Arizona%20ship%20with%20American%20flag%20above%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671faedc01ea6d83dee47c0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20booked%20a%20tour%20through%20Aulani%20because%20we%20could%20not%20get%20reservations%20to%20visit%20the%20USS%20Arizona%20Memorial%20any%20other%20way%20and%20really%20wanted%20to%20see%20it%20before%20we%20left.%3Cp%3EJill%20Robbins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20only%20so%20many%20days%20in%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20we%20really%20wanted%20to%20visit%20Pearl%20Harbor%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flast-survivor-uss-arizona-pearl-harbor-dead-at-102-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSS%20Arizona%20Memorial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETickets%20to%20the%20USS%20Arizona%20only%20cost%20%241%20to%20reserve%2C%20but%20they%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20snag%20during%20high%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20couldn't%20get%20any%20so%20we%20booked%20a%20tour%20through%20Aulani%20for%20about%20%241%2C000%20that%20included%20breakfast%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20entrance%20to%20the%20USS%20Arizona%20Memorial%20and%20Walt%20Disney%20Studios%20and%20World%20War%20II%20pop-up%20exhibit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20regret%20the%20experience%2C%20but%20that%20price%20was%20way%20above%20what%20we'd%20typically%20pay%20for%20a%20museum%20day%2C%20let%20alone%20one%20that%20could've%20cost%20us%20a%20few%20dollars.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20were%20things%20to%20do%20at%20the%20resort%20and%20we%20did%20a%20low-cost%20hike%20on%20our%20own.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%