%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20India%2C%20goat%20milk%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20staple%20due%20to%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20low%20resource%20requirements%20compared%20to%20cows.%20Goats%20are%20easier%20to%20raise%2C%20making%20them%20an%20ideal%20dairy%20option%20for%20small%20farmers%20and%20herders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMannat%20and%20Eknoor%E2%80%99s%20venture%20not%20only%20fulfils%20a%20personal%20need%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20the%20local%20economy%20and%20promotes%20healthier%20dietary%20choices.%20The%20whole%20family%20is%20supportive%20of%20their%20venture%2C%20contributing%20to%20various%20tasks.%20%E2%80%9CEverybody%20is%20involved%20somehow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mannat%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Mannat%20and%20Eknoor%20Mehmi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730896526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-25-at-4.07.44-PM-2-1730890451.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D374657%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20Goat%20Milk%20Farm%2C%20which%20began%20just%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20started%20after%20a%20personal%20health%20crisis%20when%20Mannat%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20jaundice.%20A%20well-meaning%20elder%20suggested%20that%20goat%20milk%20could%20help%20in%20her%20recovery%2C%20leading%20their%20father%2C%20Harbhajan%20Singh%2C%20to%20invest%20Rs%2020%2C000%20in%20a%20single%20goat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374657%2Fmannat-mehmi-eknoor-bahadurgarh-india-goat-milk-farm-sisters-entrepreneurship-health-benefits-saanen-goats-sustainable-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%201%20Woman%20Is%20Empowering%20Sangti%20in%20the%20Eastern%20Himalayas%20To%20Become%20a%20Zero-Waste%20Village%22%2C%22content%22%3A