ibilities%20dictated%20recipes%2C%20in%20Central%20and%20Eastern%20India%2C%20it%20was%20royal%20customs%20that%20did.%20This%20is%20what%20Tarana%20discovered%20during%20her%20stay%20at%20Bhopal%E2%80%99s%20Jehan%20Numa%20Palace%20Hotel%20%E2%80%94%20which%20belongs%20to%20the%20descendants%20of%20Nawab%20Sultan%20Jahan%20Begum%E2%80%99s%20second%20son%2C%20Nawab%20Muhammad%20Obaidullah%20Khan%2C%20and%20is%20known%20for%20its%20preservation%20of%20heirloom%20recipes%20of%20Bhopal%E2%80%99s%20Nawabi%20cuisine.%20Here%2C%20she%20enjoyed%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20two%20dishes%20with%20a%20rich%20history%3A%20the%20%3Cem%3EBhopali%20rezala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chicken%20cooked%20with%20spinach)%20%E2%80%94%20which%20she%20learnt%2C%20amalgamates%20the%20local%20flavours%20with%20%3Cem%3EAwadhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Mughal%20cuisine%20and%20is%20popular%20in%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Efilfora%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20unique%20mincemeat%20preparation).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20more%20about%20these%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBhopalis%20apparently%20prepared%20%3Cem%3Erezala%20%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20peacock%20meat%20until%20hunting%20peacocks%20was%20banned.%20As%20for%20%3Cem%3Efilfora%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20has%20its%20roots%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349748%2Flaal-maas-history-recipe-best-places-to-eat-in-rajasthan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehunting%20traditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Bhopal.%20Upon%20the%20killing%20of%20an%20animal%20%E2%80%93%20usually%20nilgai%2C%20deer%20or%20gazelle%20%E2%80%93%20its%20meat%20was%20coarsely%20chopped%20or%20sliced%20into%20slivers%20while%20still%20warm%2C%20and%20imme