ta-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20problem%20of%20accessibility%20remains%2C%20the%20other%20concern%20is%20affordability.%20To%20provide%20dialysis%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Programme%20(PMNDP)%20was%20rolled%20out%20in%20April%202016.%20The%20programme%20has%20two%20components%3A%20Hemodialysis%20(HD)%20services%20and%20Peritoneal%20dialysis%20(PD)%20services.%20Under%20the%20PMNDP%2C%20the%20government%20has%20set%20up%201%2C530%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20still%20leaving%20a%20significant%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKey%20issues%20include%20high%20treatment%20costs%2C%20limited%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344858%2Fthe-hans-foundation-dialysis-chronic-kidney-disease-renal-care-centre-treat-underprivileged-rural-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accessibility%20barriers%20for%20patients%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20healthcare%20professionals.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20kidney%20disease%20and%20dialysis%20options%20further%20complicates%20timely%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20Dialysis%20Convenient%3A%20How%20VitusCare%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVitusCare%20provides%20three%20forms%20of%20patient%20care%3A%20the%20in-centre%20dialysis%20model%2C%20where%20they%20set%20up%20centres%20inside%20existing%20hospitals%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20cities%20(95%20percent%20of%20their%20centres)%2C%20standalone%20centres%20where%20they%20open%20facilities%20in%20areas%20without%20hospitals%2C%20and%20at-home%20dialysis%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20their%20most%20popular%20form%20of%20care%2C%20the%20in-centre%20dialysis%20model%2C%20Prabhat%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20identify%20a%20space%2C%20develop%20and%20prepare%20it.%20We%20employ%20support%20staff%20in%20the%20centres.%20Using%20a%20hub-and-spoke%20model%2C%20we%20monitor%20all%20centres%20through%20our%20central%20team%20in%20Gurgaon.%20We%20have%20an%20operations%20team%20that%20monitors%20each%20centre%2C%20ensuring%20quality%20through%20strict%20SOPs.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Ffit%3D1600%252C739%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22VitusCare%20works%20on%20a%20box-in-box%20model.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fw%3D1600%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fresize%3D300%252C139%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fresize%3D500%252C231%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fresize%3D768%252C355%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fresize%3D1536%252C709%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvitus-1730297981.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C69%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVitusCare%20works%20on%20a%20box-in-box%20model%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20model%2C%20the%20company%20owns%20all%20the%20assets%20and%20directly%20manages%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20dialysis%20centre.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20allows%20us%20to%20maintain%20stringent%20quality%20standards%20and%20ensure%20consistency%20in%20patient%20care%20across%20all%20locations%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Prabhat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20clinical%20team%2C%20a%20biomedical%20team%2C%20administrative%20staff%2C%20a%20network%20of%20delivery%20therapists%2C%20nurses%2C%20nephrologists%2C%20operations%20teams%2C%20and%20teams%20that%20focus%20on%20increasing%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20mission%20is%20to%20bring%20dialysis%20centres%20near%20the%20patients%E2%80%99%20home%2C%20minimising%20travel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVitusCare%20provides%20free%20dialysis%20for%20patients%20under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20kidney%20disease%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20reverse.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20kidney%20has%20failed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20failed.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20cure%20CKD%20stage%20two%20or%20three%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatients%20have%20two%20options%3A%20opting%20for%20kidney%20transplants%20or%20undergoing%20dialysis.%20The%20former%20is%20expensive%20and%20comes%20with%20the%20added%20problem%20of%20lack%20of%20donors.%20For%20most%20patients%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20the%20only%20viable%20option%20to%20ensure%20a%20good%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMissing%20dialysis%20sessions%20can%20lead%20to%20serious%20health%20complications%20as%20waste%20and%20fluids%20build%20up%20in%20the%20body.%20High%20potassium%20levels%20can%20disrupt%20heart%20rhythm%20and%20become%20life-threatening.%20Fluid%20overload%20may%20cause%20fluid%20retention%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20leading%20to%20breathlessness%2C%20swollen%20ankles%2C%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20and%20even%20heart%20failure.%20Patients%20may%20also%20experience%20intense%20itching%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%2C%20and%20reduced%20appetite%2C%20further%20weakening%20their%20overall%20health.%20Regular%20dialysis%20is%20essential%20to%20manage%20these%20risks%20and%20maintain%20stability%20for%20those%20with%20kidney%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20bootstrapped%2C%20the%20founders%20recently%20managed%20to%20raise%20a%20Series%20A%20round%20of%20investment.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20currently%20have%20centres%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20plan%20to%20deepen%20their%20presence%20in%20these%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20journey%20has%20been%20very%20satisfying%20and%20full%20of%20learning.%20We%20want%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekidney%20disease%20patients%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20concludes%20Prabhat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flanglo%2Farticle%2FPIIS2214-109X(16)30308-4%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5